data.description: Pointe 2022 Resale, the Santa Barbara floor plan. 3-bed, 2-bath home with a completed front and backyard landscaping. Located in the sought-after Paseos of Mission Ridge, just off Eastlake Blvd. The seller invested $18,000 in landscaping the front and backyard with artificial grass and stamped cement, offering a perfect space for a pergola or jacuzzi. This corner lot property provides room for RV parking. Inside, you'll find elegant tile flooring, quartz countertops, and crisp white shaker cabinets. The open-concept living area is ideal for everyday living and entertaining, with a spacious kitchen featuring an island and all appliances, including a stainless refrigerator. Shutters adorn every window, and the subdivision offers access to a private homeowners association pool for outdoor enjoyment. Plus, a new Albertsons is just 2 minutes away.
